name: pharosvpn
origin: security/pharosvpn
version: "%%VERSION%%"
comment: PharosVPN userspace AmneziaWG data-plane daemon (pharos-awg)
maintainer: dev@pharosvpn.invalid
www: https://github.com/PharosVPN
abi: "FreeBSD:14:amd64"
arch: "freebsd:14:x86:64"
prefix: /usr/local
licenselogic: single
licenses: [APACHE20]
desc: <<EOD
PharosVPN userspace AmneziaWG (amneziawg-go) data-plane daemon for FreeBSD /
OPNsense. Ships pharos-awg to /usr/local/sbin plus a configd-managed rc.d script.
It runs a caravel obfuscated-WireGuard tunnel over a FreeBSD tun, applies host
addressing/routing, and serves the wireguard UAPI socket for status tooling.

Required at runtime by the os-pharosvpn OPNsense plugin. Expects the if_tuntap
driver (resident in the OPNsense kernel).
EOD
categories: [security]
